description:
The cast head to New York for the Summer. Lucy is feeling alienated by the rest of the girls and befriends fashion blogger Billie. Spencer and Jamie are both interested in Billie right away, but Lucy has other ideas and tries setting her up with Stevie, who's now single. Binky catches up with Rosie and Louise to tell them why Alex isn't with her. Proudlock and Stevie through a party, were Proudlock has a chance to introduce Louise to his friend Alec. Binky is soon forced to confront previous issues with both Lucy and Cheska.
